      "rationale": "Mean absolute error on NIH is 8.3% across 5 operating points. Experimental uncertainty bars overlap CFD predictions at 4 of 5 points. One outlier at high-speed low-flow condition (MAE 14%) attributed to transitional flow regime not fully captured by SST model."
